":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb5b36c8a75df048548aec13a5ebe9de161137a0","tid":241788,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人真係好悲哀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n變相 birth control <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後又將人口老化問題歸咎於年輕人不願生育<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7fa4f2bab934cd1877df935000b5b4dea1e000","tid":241788,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89ffbcc986ab424a2ce699a225b0484b41224f62","tid":241788,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"唔夠錢養又無時間湊就唔好學人生啦<br />\n仲要充大頭生夠兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55b4d69771e0f4692847f6ce290bf54bd9dacec","tid":241788,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:52:40.000Z","msg":"佢哋希望小朋友多啲活動空間同遊玩設施<br />\n<br />\n得200幾呎仲咁多要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n真係為個細路好就帶佢落公園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfa295a5822f3ca92a74ab93ef8ac3bb713a99d","tid":241788,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠錢養又無時間湊就唔好學人生啦<br />\n仲要充大頭生夠兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錢就唔會買到層樓又請到工人同用45萬裝修啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n層嘢大大話話都400幾萬呀<br />\n噉都充大頭鬼？<br />\n原來香港而家通脹到連小康都變窮撚啦？"},{"pid":"51ba3a55aa05c56bcf1abc4bd3b154ee029faa80","tid":241788,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兩公婆住都嫌細<br />\n仲要生多兩個B加個工人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有咩問題呢？人哋都話只係住幾年，應該只係為咗個校網，話唔定人哋原本住緊千幾呎呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩校網咁巴閉<br />\n<br />\n沙田友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係依家呢個抄賣，投資，做保險就會發達既年代！屌你老尾，仲幫小朋友搵學校網，真心覺得佢地岸尻！晒埋啲咁既錢，不如直接<span style=\"color: red;\">陪養</span>個仔，考地產牌，保險牌，仲撚實際啦！ 有錢之後慢慢買學歷好撚過啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時菲律賓碩士，博士！大把有得你簡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晒錢？人地買完層樓到個仔，分分鐘個仔升小一就升多一個double啦，而且<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔洗住呀？</span><br />\n陪養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家香港唔做嘢搵幾萬幾二萬蚊個月，陪個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋小學就考地產牌、保險牌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwhy not both？小學唔讀，考地產同保險，到中學就可以執業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時間仲可以炒埋樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時中6就可以買博士啦嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04aa3fb62737557e9aa9d4e836258626229fbbb5","tid":241788,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"主流傳媒日日出文教港豬幾細㗎樓都是要買"},{"pid":"fff21ecbeb905d9e777163b974b08f6f5d6ea471","tid":241788,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:26:22.000Z